{"data":{"page":{"html":"<h1 id=\"call-and-user-defined-handlers\"><a href=\"#call-and-user-defined-handlers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Call and user defined handlers</h1>\n<div class=\"toc\">\n<h2><a href=\"#toc\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Table of Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#introduction\">Introduction</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#calling-a-function\">Calling a function</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#calling-a-module\">Calling a module</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"introduction\"><a href=\"#introduction\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Introduction</h2>\n<p>Nikita gives you the choice between calling your own function, which we call handlers, or calling an <a href=\"./registered_handlers\">registered function</a> by its name.</p>\n<h2 id=\"calling-a-function\"><a href=\"#calling-a-function\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Calling a function</h2>\n<p>In its simplest form, user defined handler is just a function passed to \"call\". Here's an illustration:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">nikita\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  fs<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">touch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>file<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>This is internally converted to:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">nikita\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  handler<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    fs<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">touch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>file<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Use the expanded object syntax to pass additional information. For example, we could add the retry option:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">nikita\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  retry<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  handler<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    fs<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">touch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>file<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Note, the above code could be arguably simplified using 2 arguments:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">nikita\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  retry<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  fs<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">touch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>file<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"calling-a-module\"><a href=\"#calling-a-module\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Calling a module</h2>\n<p>If no handler is yet defined, a string is interpreted as an external module exporting a handler function or object. The 3 calls below are all equivalents:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">nikita\n<span class=\"token comment\">// String with an additionnal option object</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token string\">'path/to/module'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  retry<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Expanded object syntax</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  handler<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'path/to/module'</span>\n  retry<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Internally, module are required with the call <code class=\"language-text\">require.main.require</code>.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/usages/call/","edit_url":"https://github.com/adaltas/node-nikita-docs/edit/master/src/md/usages/call.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Call","description":null,"keywords":null}}},"pageContext":{}}